              We build the pipes, not the products
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-dark leading-relaxed" style="max-width: 55ch;">
              <p>
                PrimeBridge is not a fund. We don't pool capital. We don't set underwriting. We don't own the credit.
              </p>
              <p class="text-darkest font-semibold">
                We build the pipes that enable lenders and investors to transact with clarity, speed, and confidence.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-light p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-6">Our platform provides:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Tape ingestion & standardization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Automated validation & analytics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Instant deal room creation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Investor soft-commit workflows</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Clear, fast feedback loops</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-dark">Dedicated support for both sides</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
